It's a similar type of interface.

00:04:52.810 --> 00:04:54.110
It's context sensitive.

00:04:54.110 --> 00:04:54.960
It's floating.

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:56.090
It's transparent.

00:04:56.100 --> 00:05:00.080
You can move it around in your
workspace to have it where you need it.

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:03.100
And it changes based on whatever
it is you're currently using.

00:05:03.100 --> 00:05:06.100
