it changes the scale widget.

00:05:06.100 --> 00:05:08.820
If you're using a spin behavior,
it updates with the spin

00:05:08.820 --> 00:05:10.100
behavior you see here.

00:05:10.130 --> 00:05:13.300
Also we have on-screen controls
for all the transformation scale

00:05:13.300 --> 00:05:16.830
and rotation so you can dynamically
resize things in the canvas window.

00:05:17.100 --> 00:05:20.060
