00:06:47.740 --> 00:06:50.660
We also support nested layers,
which is incredibly important these days

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:53.990
because blend modes can get very complex,
and you can have logos that

00:06:53.990 --> 00:06:57.100
are made up of 10 layers,
and that gets incorporated with a piece

00:06:57.100 --> 00:06:58.270
of footage or something like that.

00:06:58.610 --> 00:07:02.550
All of those elements can
be independently animated,

00:07:02.550 --> 00:07:07.500
but in the smallest context we have
a layer list that affords you to

00:07:07.500 --> 00:07:10.710
reposition those in the visual queue.

00:07:11.590 --> 00:07:14.610
Templates are,
we actually ship with templates,

00:07:14.650 --> 00:07:18.100
